{"tid":1534672,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"天后必食泰國菜","createTime":"2019-09-03T05:33:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T05:33:27.000Z","uid":285421,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1ecf6999aa2f34a3385a17430d27c8628cb515e2","tid":1534672,"uid":285421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:33:09.000Z","msg":"話說啱啱放學去泰味屋食飯<br />\n埋單果陣老闆娘見我地戴住白絲帶同黑口罩<br />\n同我地細細聲講左句加油<br />\n本身已經覺得好好味架啦而家仲多左一份人情味<br />\nbtw呢間嘢係天后地鐵站附近近坑口方向<br />\n下次遊行前可以去填飽個肚先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/09/03/133100_ca5429500a0578932067e6229d37e620.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F09%2F03%2F133100_ca5429500a0578932067e6229d37e620.png&h=9153bada&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b30cb04cde444406e280372ab8f1272cfe405401","tid":1534672,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:33:27.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\